org.osmdroid.tileprovider.modules

Class MapTileFilesystemProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osmdroid.tileprovider.modules.MapTileModuleProviderBase
      • org.osmdroid.tileprovider.modules.MapTileFileStorageProviderBase
        • org.osmdroid.tileprovider.modules.MapTileFilesystemProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OpenStreetMapTileProviderConstants

    public class MapTileFilesystemProvider
extends MapTileFileStorageProviderBase
    Implements a file system cache and provides cached tiles. This functions as a tile provider by serving cached tiles for the supplied tile source.
    Author:
    Marc Kurtz, Nicolas Gramlich
